{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/steam_attack_on_mutation_station_3d_exploration.gif?t=1732255541\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unravel a genre-hopping mystery about neon spaceships, alien plants, digital demigods, and the nature of reality in... Attack on Mutation Station.</strong>     </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/steam_attack_on_mutation_station_point_and_click.gif?t=1732255541\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Premise:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are an elite pilot, sent to eliminate an alien, plant-like organism that has taken over a space research station. The game starts out as a colorful and campy sci-fi space shooter, but quickly turns into more of a mystery investigation as different gameplay elements are introduced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/steam_attack_on_mutation_station_shoot_em_up.gif?t=1732255541\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Your job is to...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Exterminate any mutated plants on site, in glorious shoot 'em up sections inspired by classic shooter games from the 80s and 90s.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Investigate the space station, and uncover the truth about y\u0334\u033d\u0328\u2588\u0337\u0303\u0321\u2588\u0336\u0341\u034e\u2588\u0334\u0357\u0359 \u0338\u030e\u032cm\u0335\u0350\u032e\u2588\u0334\u0344\u0320\u2588\u0334\u0344\u0333\u2588\u0336\u0307\u0324\u2588\u0337\u0303\u0354\u2588\u0334\u035d\u0359\u2588\u0335\u0344\u035c\u2588\u0338\u0312\u0333  in classic 2D point &amp; click adventure fashion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Question everything, and discover the t\u0336\u0360\u030d\u0332\u2588\u0334\u0346\u031d\u2588\u0338\u030b\u0347\u2588\u0338\u0312\u033f\u0323\u0322\u0332 \u0336\u0301\u034e\u033a\u2588\u0335\u0342\u0317\u2588\u0334\u0352\u0306\u031dt\u0334\u0341\u033d\u0331\u2588\u0337\u0314\u034c\u033f\u0349\u032b\u2588\u0334\u0360\u0310\u035a\u032ee\u0335\u0358\u0355\u0317 \u0336\u034b\u033b\u0326\u2588\u0334\u031a\u0305\u0326\u032b\u2588\u0338\u0305\u0333\u0326 \u0336\u0360\u0357\u0300\u0316\u033br\u0335\u035d\u0300\u033f\u0327\u2588\u0337\u033d\u034b\u0303\u035a\u0356\u2588\u0335\u0306\u030e\u0354\u0324\u2588\u0335\u034c\u0314\u0348i\u0337\u0310\u0319\u0318\u032f\u2588\u0336\u033f\u030c\u0349\u2588\u0338\u0304\u0304\u0348\u032d  by exploring the station in first-person perspective.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn that there is more to this mission, and to this game, than meets the eye.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/steam_attack_on_mutation_station_glitches.gif?t=1732255541\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You may encounter occasional \u2588\u0338\u034c\u0332\u031e\u2588\u0338\u033f\u0357\u0350\u033f\u0348\u0348\u2588\u0335\u0350\u0355\u0353\u033b\u2588\u0334\u030a\u0353\u0347\u032e\u031f\u2588\u0337\u0344\u0360\u033f\u0303\u0326\u034e\u0318\u031d\u2588\u0338\u0311\u0341\u035d\u030c\u0339\u0345\u0319\u0330\u2588\u0336\u0343\u030a\u030e\u0315\u031e\u2588\u0338\u030b\u034c\u0330\u035a\u0359 but don't worry, it's all part of the \u2588\u0334\u0301\u0302\u0359\u033c\u031e\u0330\u032d\u2588\u0335\u031b\u0314\u0324\u0325\u2588\u0336\u0351\u034a\u033f\u0303\u0316\u2588\u0335\u0309\u035d\u033e\u0354\u0323.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057110/extras/steam_attack_on_mutation_station_may_the_patron_guide_your_way.gif?t=1732255541\" /></p>","backgro